Each UI element is connected to the signup process where the user inputs their information.

Elements:
1. Avatar â†’ displays the user profile picture
2. ProgressBar â†’ shows loading process
3. TextInputLayout + EditText â†’ fields for First Name, Last Name, Username, and Password
4. Signup Button â†’ triggers the signup function
5. Login Link â†’ navigates to login screen if the user already has an account
